('ZewrhKT-qBQxT1eNoBWFP', 'Primal Radiance', '[{\"type\": \"increasedamagegiven\", \"power\": 15, \"target\": \"INHERIT\", \"direction\": \"offence\", \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Increase Damage done\", \"powerPerLevel\": 1, \"appearAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAssetPath\": \"\", \"disappearAnimation\": \"\"}, {\"type\": \"increasedamagetaken\", \"power\": 10, \"target\": \"INHERIT\", \"elements\": [\"Water\"], \"direction\": \"offence\", \"statTypes\": [], \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Adjust damage taken of target\", \"generalTypes\": [], \"powerPerLevel\": 1, \"appearAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAssetPath\": \"\", \"disappearAnimation\": \"\"}]', 'One of the most Modern bloodlines to have formed, the origins of this are well documented. It was stated that the father of beast style signed a contract with the beast kingdom, this contract entailed a blood fusion that allows the members of this bloodline to channel the primal energy  into devastating taijutsu.', 10, 'All', 'https://utfs.io/f/aa25ae7e-b322-456d-b260-e3e6920bbeb4-kbo8g4.jpg', '2023-08-29 06:19:58.541', '2023-08-29 06:19:58.541', 'B', 0),
('zOGMXO1nnBTEE0sAJRCuD', 'Voltara Divine', '[{\"type\": \"increasedamagegiven\", \"power\": 15, \"target\": \"INHERIT\", \"direction\": \"offence\", \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Adjust damage given by target\", \"powerPerLevel\": 1, \"appearAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAssetPath\": \"\", \"disappearAnimation\": \"\"}, {\"type\": \"increasedamagetaken\", \"power\": 10, \"target\": \"INHERIT\", \"elements\": [\"Wind\"], \"direction\": \"offence\", \"statTypes\": [], \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Adjust damage taken of target\", \"generalTypes\": [], \"powerPerLevel\": 1, \"appearAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAnimation\": \"\", \"staticAssetPath\": \"\", \"disappearAnimation\": \"\"}]', 'Legend says that the members of this bloodline are descendants of a lightning deity thought by some to be the sacred Raijin himself. According to more obscure rumors, a god with a voice that roared like thunder once descended from the heavens and proclaimed that he would no longer wish to walk among his kin, choosing the human world as his new abode. The deity is said to have wed a human and sired a child who inherited their father\'s fearsome power to bend lightning to their will.', 10, '', 'https://uploadthing.com/f/c213746a-66d1-4334-80b9-e5ecfd30ae7d_1000003682.jpg', '2023-08-29 04:00:01.867', '2023-08-29 04:00:01.867', 'B', 0);
